Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.39,0:00:07.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,见不到矢野了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.40,0:00:12.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暑假过得好无聊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.68,0:00:26.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.15,0:00:27.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.71,0:00:29.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都到齐了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.71,0:00:31.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先把桌子搬到前面去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.55,0:00:33.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野 去厕所了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.38,0:00:36.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 是矢野
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.92,0:00:37.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他说今儿不来了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.64,0:00:39.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.93,0:00:40.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.76,0:00:42.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能去排练了 找人代演一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.19,0:00:47.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有主角怎么开始排练 把他叫过来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.80,0:00:49.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他关机了 没法了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.96,0:00:51.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一点责任感都没
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.51,0:00:52.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.17,0:00:53.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那小子该做的一定会做
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.73,0:00:55.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是这个问题啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.53,0:00:57.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 人家明明很期待的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.10,0:01:17.00,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}嘘つきなあなた 泣き虫のあたし
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.05,0:01:22.90,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}どうして？ うまくいかないわ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.14,0:01:28.87,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}オシャレした髪も ラインストーンの爪も
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.13,0:01:34.77,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}あなたは気付きもしないね
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.07,0:01:41.90,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}LOVE 悲しい涙なんかじゃないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.34,0:01:46.90,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}目が乾いてヒリヒリするだけ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.15,0:01:49.86,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}転んでばっかり I LOVE
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.98,0:02:01.40,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}君だけを あたしだけを
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.93,0:02:06.38,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}熱い想いを受け止めて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.96,0:02:13.57,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}どこまでも つながってたい
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.08,0:02:18.40,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}可愛くない泣き顔も
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.64,0:02:20.42,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}全部愛してね
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.10,0:01:17.00,op_chs,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}谎话连篇的你 爱哭鼻子的我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.05,0:01:22.90,op_chs,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}怎么进展得不顺利呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.14,0:01:28.87,op_chs,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}精心打扮的头发 光彩夺目的指甲
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.13,0:01:34.77,op_chs,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}你却都没注意到
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.07,0:01:41.90,op_chs,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}love 并非悲伤的泪水
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.34,0:01:46.90,op_chs,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}干涩的眼睛只是有些刺痛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.15,0:01:53.16,op_chs,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}泪水滚落不停 I love
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.98,0:02:01.40,op_chs,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}只有你 只有我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.93,0:02:06.38,op_chs,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}理解那炽热的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.96,0:02:13.57,op_chs,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}无论在哪里 都彼此相连
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.08,0:02:18.40,op_chs,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}连你并不可爱的哭脸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.64,0:02:20.42,op_chs,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}我也深爱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.59,0:02:35.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果 之后的排练矢野也没来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.24,0:02:39.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.21,0:02:41.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 小水
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.85,0:02:42.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祭典
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.91,0:02:44.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我去 我去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.64,0:02:46.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 要穿浴衣去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.46,0:02:48.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唔 那我还是算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.50,0:02:49.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,约了矢野他们的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.97,0:02:55.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,排练偷懒 这种时候倒去了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.35,0:02:58.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,见到了一定要狠狠教训他
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.95,0:03:00.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.77,0:03:02.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮我把浴衣拿出来 浴衣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.61,0:03:09.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶 七七也穿了浴衣耶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.72,0:03:11.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 来晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.46,0:03:14.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七七 今天看起来非常可爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.13,0:03:15.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.01,0:03:17.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浴衣很衬你 吓了我一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.07,0:03:19.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这颜色也很适合
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.10,0:03:21.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很合适吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.81,0:03:26.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这件是向表姐借的 我自己那件太孩子气了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.93,0:03:28.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腮红也非常可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.53,0:03:29.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿嘿 是杏桃色
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.03,0:03:31.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像刚泡完澡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.48,0:03:33.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇啊 是浴衣啊 浴衣军团
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.45,0:03:34.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔 男生们来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.88,0:03:36.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 矢野呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.67,0:03:39.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个啥 他的手机一直打不通
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.59,0:03:40.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.45,0:03:42.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 我想他大概会和家门口的朋友一起来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.88,0:03:44.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过会儿就会碰见吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.53,0:03:46.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他要是来 多好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.33,0:03:49.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 高桥 你简直像换了个人似的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.41,0:03:49.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.85,0:03:51.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧 她穿浴衣很好看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.80,0:03:53.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿嘿 没有啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.31,0:03:55.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说娃娃脸小个子意外地适合穿和服
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.09,0:03:59.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想想平时的高桥 真觉得被骗了似的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.49,0:04:00.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 好可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.68,0:04:02.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,制服要是浴衣的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.56,0:04:04.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没准很受欢迎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.51,0:04:08.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 矢野你在搞什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.36,0:04:14.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七七 你可以得到一个的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.77,0:04:15.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 给
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.48,0:04:16.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.93,0:04:18.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.74,0:04:20.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七七
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.65,0:04:22.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竹内君
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.41,0:04:26.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吓了我一跳 我还以为是谁呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.65,0:04:27.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿 好久不见啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.77,0:04:28.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和谁来的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.90,0:04:30.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和班上的同学
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.66,0:04:31.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竹内君 你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.95,0:04:33.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和邻居一起来的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.46,0:04:36.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙 没来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.61,0:04:39.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶 我又不是问这个
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.74,0:04:43.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真坦率啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.48,0:04:46.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说矢野没来？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.16,0:04:49.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙好像不太需要别人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.80,0:04:51.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我也说不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.21,0:04:54.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得我们不管怎么闹 怎么玩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.12,0:04:56.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他都好像无所谓一样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.88,0:04:59.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是他感觉不到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.07,0:05:03.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是他时常空虚呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.25,0:05:06.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像不管我们做什么都是白费工夫
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.23,0:05:10.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鼓起勇气穿上浴衣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.79,0:05:13.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掰着手指头算着排练的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.03,0:05:15.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是徒劳吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.76,0:05:20.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七七 吃刨冰吗 我去买
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.06,0:05:24.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 我还是联系不到他
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.44,0:05:25.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 没关系的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.46,0:05:27.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只想抱怨一下他不来排练的事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.31,0:05:36.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为 是忌日
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.56,0:05:40.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前天是奈奈的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.62,0:05:44.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他还是难过吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.83,0:05:50.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 完全不知道这事儿
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.15,0:05:56.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么都不知道 一个人兴奋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.89,0:05:58.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样比较好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.70,0:06:01.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有精力旺盛的人在他周围玩闹比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.39,0:06:06.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的开朗分他一些就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.26,0:06:09.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.14,0:06:10.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回见
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.54,0:06:18.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你穿浴衣很可爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.28,0:06:34.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 能做些什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.59,0:06:42.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我会在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.22,0:06:49.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.70,0:06:52.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都不知道和他说什么好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.59,0:06:54.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔 跟踪狂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.27,0:06:55.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在别人家门前晃来晃去的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.75,0:06:59.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.96,0:07:01.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 我不是跟踪狂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.07,0:07:03.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吓死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.44,0:07:05.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶 那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.12,0:07:06.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他什么时候看见的 什么时候
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.80,0:07:08.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是找你有事的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.52,0:07:09.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来我周围晃来晃去？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.96,0:07:11.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的 你看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.38,0:07:13.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我进去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.36,0:07:14.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敝宅拒绝变态
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.33,0:07:19.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙 矢野 你快点给我开门
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.20,0:07:20.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女变态恼羞成怒啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.67,0:07:21.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.31,0:07:24.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野太太 我是来给府上臭白痴儿子做家庭访问的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.49,0:07:25.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点给我开门吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.65,0:07:28.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你久等了 不好意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.95,0:07:30.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 糗大了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.78,0:07:33.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请慢用
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.94,0:07:37.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.75,0:07:39.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.26,0:07:45.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在矢野的房间里两人独处
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.70,0:07:47.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 好紧张
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.72,0:07:49.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高桥 你是来查什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.81,0:07:54.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 我是想你是不是病了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.03,0:07:56.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你会觉得我病了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.02,0:07:58.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你一直没来排练
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.62,0:08:02.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你直接问我为什么不去排练不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.59,0:08:04.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直偷懒还这么了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.91,0:08:06.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你为什么不来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.57,0:08:07.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀 糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.13,0:08:10.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.99,0:08:14.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沉浸在对奈奈的回忆里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.04,0:08:16.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一到夏天我就不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.75,0:08:24.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 后天还有大后天的排练能请假吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.01,0:08:28.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你骗人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.48,0:08:31.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底为什么不来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.51,0:08:34.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是暑假 早上九点哪起得来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.80,0:08:36.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这个家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.35,0:08:37.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,替你担心真是亏了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.39,0:08:40.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你吃到了水羊羹不也挺好嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.43,0:08:42.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又不是为了吃水羊羹才来的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.53,0:08:43.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你别吃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.30,0:08:44.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我偏要吃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.88,0:08:48.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊 不是挺精神嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.34,0:08:51.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.24,0:08:56.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 终于见到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.81,0:08:59.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那是相册？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.84,0:09:00.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.42,0:09:00.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.01,0:09:01.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.75,0:09:02.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.63,0:09:04.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下我把不好的照片拿掉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.34,0:09:05.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么不好的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.24,0:09:07.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修学旅行去的是札幌么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.87,0:09:09.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我们一样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.55,0:09:13.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.38,0:09:17.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈奈的照片 给我看一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.75,0:09:20.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看这个要干吗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.91,0:09:23.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.61,0:09:28.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看了 又想怎样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.07,0:09:30.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我自己都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.16,0:09:33.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真不小心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.70,0:09:33.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.93,0:09:35.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道你现在在哪儿吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.20,0:09:38.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在床上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.17,0:09:42.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可 可是门开着
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.58,0:09:45.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,窗子也是 外面一直有人过
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.53,0:09:48.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野你又是同班同学
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.74,0:09:52.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你搞什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.09,0:09:58.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事 我什么也没干 是她自己跌倒的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.06,0:10:00.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打 打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.26,0:10:04.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋啊 别当真呀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.30,0:10:08.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊 是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.81,0:10:11.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是奈奈的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.20,0:10:14.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的照片我一张都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.74,0:10:19.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他一点也不为所动
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.16,0:10:23.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每天 我都在想你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.73,0:10:25.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高高兴兴地去排练
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.85,0:10:27.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还鼓起勇气穿上了浴衣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.26,0:10:29.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还上门来找你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.88,0:10:33.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是这些事 好像都与你无关
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.38,0:10:36.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后天的排练一定要来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.84,0:10:38.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能说的只有这一句了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.24,0:10:40.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我们只是普通同学
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.00,0:10:43.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高桥 今天 谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.12,0:10:46.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想见你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.01,0:10:48.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.19,0:10:52.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野你非常非常喜欢的人可能已经不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.74,0:10:54.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可能很寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.05,0:10:58.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是非常非常喜欢你的人不是还有吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.92,0:11:00.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样正负抵消不就是零了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.68,0:11:05.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 不要觉得你孤单一人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.35,0:11:08.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会看着你的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.99,0:11:11.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会一直看着矢野你的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.40,0:11:12.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,守护着你的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.07,0:11:17.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.66,0:11:25.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会看着 一直守护着你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.32,0:11:28.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 不要觉得你孤单一人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.71,0:11:32.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去看过小道具那边了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.19,0:11:35.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蛮顺利的 因为山本同学很能干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.43,0:11:36.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 矢野呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.40,0:11:38.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天他还是没来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.83,0:11:40.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 不用指望那家伙了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.24,0:11:42.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就靠我的演技弥补吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.12,0:11:47.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘴上说起来简单 结果却什么都没变
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.19,0:11:52.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我觉得自己 好无力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.55,0:11:56.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.10,0:11:57.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.45,0:12:02.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他 来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.93,0:12:05.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七七 七七看法披
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.54,0:12:08.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们借了两件 哪个颜色好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.42,0:12:09.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红的很可爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.10,0:12:11.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然红的比较好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.16,0:12:12.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.31,0:12:14.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈 果然很可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.79,0:12:16.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弄脏了也看不出来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.33,0:12:17.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.65,0:12:18.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快看快看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.66,0:12:25.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红色的不错嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.63,0:12:26.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对是白的好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.51,0:12:32.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我这么心跳的再没别人了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.55,0:12:33.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白的好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.08,0:12:35.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白的很适合你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.65,0:12:37.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好 矢野你穿什么都合适
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.34,0:12:40.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你穿浴衣也很合适啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.70,0:12:43.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.06,0:12:50.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.79,0:12:54.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竹内传给我的 拍得蛮好的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.83,0:12:57.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我后悔那天没去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.42,0:13:05.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说过会看着我的 一直看着我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.16,0:13:07.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你办得到吗 这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.66,0:13:08.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,办 办得到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.99,0:13:12.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别开玩笑了 你也太乱来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.50,0:13:14.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么“正负得零” 哪有这种歪理啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.92,0:13:18.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,守护？说出这种男人的话 你太臭美啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.99,0:13:20.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这么说太过分了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.84,0:13:21.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.05,0:13:23.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.46,0:13:25.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.13,0:13:28.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗你的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.87,0:13:32.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实我很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.00,0:13:37.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七七
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.61,0:13:39.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.75,0:13:40.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胸口借我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.87,0:13:52.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会一直注视着你 说好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.91,0:13:55.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你并不孤单
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.46,0:14:02.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暑假很快就过去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.15,0:14:07.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我和矢野之间什么都没变
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.90,0:14:12.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野在这种地方也能睡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.66,0:14:14.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且还用我的包包作枕头
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.95,0:14:19.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是在做梦啊 无忧无虑的梦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.10,0:14:23.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野在做什么样的梦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.31,0:14:28.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是山本的姐姐吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.29,0:14:31.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和她在一起的男人不是香川么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.00,0:14:33.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们入学的那年他正好毕业？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.95,0:14:36.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙总是带着不同的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.18,0:14:38.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟无聊的人交往啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.25,0:14:40.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 被泼水了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.80,0:14:41.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惨烈啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.77,0:14:44.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.97,0:14:45.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真差劲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.02,0:14:48.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你们是有里的同学吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.55,0:14:51.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 能借我点儿钱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.98,0:14:54.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙没付账就走了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.18,0:14:58.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 加那么多辣椒酱会生痔疮的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.80,0:14:59.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痔疮吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.17,0:15:02.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大姐姐 你和你妹妹不大像哟
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.95,0:15:05.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 你觉得我是个白痴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.98,0:15:07.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是怎么回事儿
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.29,0:15:09.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 这个嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.31,0:15:10.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摔倒的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.59,0:15:12.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙每次心情不好就这样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.78,0:15:14.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很像小孩子一样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.21,0:15:18.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你男朋友的名声可是不好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.35,0:15:19.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是他很帅啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.96,0:15:21.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坏也是魅力
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.05,0:15:23.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世上就没有完美的人嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.21,0:15:26.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要我能理解他就好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.90,0:15:29.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这就是盲目啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.65,0:15:31.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明没有真心喜欢过别人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.87,0:15:34.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这才叫做乳臭未干啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.96,0:15:36.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也快谈一次真正的恋爱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.12,0:15:45.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 奈奈在等她男朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.31,0:15:47.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找个暖和点的地方等多好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.08,0:15:49.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没钱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.14,0:15:50.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别看她 要不又敲诈你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.80,0:15:52.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天干吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.90,0:15:54.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去竹内家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.20,0:15:55.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我先回去换下衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.00,0:15:56.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.36,0:15:58.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 Sunday出刊了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.70,0:16:00.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈 这是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.04,0:16:03.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有趣 真好笑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.63,0:16:08.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还以为他会来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.74,0:16:09.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.89,0:16:11.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你还等什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.35,0:16:12.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了积攒怨气
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.01,0:16:13.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怨气
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.12,0:16:16.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了积攒怨气然后咒死他
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.11,0:16:19.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别小看女人喔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.12,0:16:25.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐 那个不是怀炉 是喝的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.99,0:16:39.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是他说不让我和别的男人说话的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.22,0:16:41.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就回了句“你不也和那女的上床了吗”
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.16,0:16:43.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是就被他打了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.78,0:16:45.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙完全乐在其中
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.12,0:16:46.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每一次我哭
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.16,0:16:50.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就沉浸在“又有女人为我哭了”的自我陶醉中
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.70,0:16:51.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去死吧 笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.61,0:16:55.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我咒你从天桥上掉下来摔断脖子 让卸货车碾脑袋碾死
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.97,0:16:57.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也说句话吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.88,0:16:58.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.77,0:17:01.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正你一定会想我是个白痴对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.83,0:17:05.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 我该怎么办好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.89,0:17:08.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？自己的事情自己考虑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.80,0:17:11.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是白痴啊 想不出来嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.26,0:17:14.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我告诉你也可以
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.67,0:17:18.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 你绝对要按我说的做
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.32,0:17:23.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样会让我幸福吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.81,0:17:27.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸福 是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.70,0:17:29.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.72,0:17:35.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概 是谁都不哭泣 不生气吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.33,0:17:38.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有打架没有乱扔东西的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.82,0:17:39.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.37,0:17:41.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.61,0:17:42.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.66,0:17:45.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.49,0:17:48.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们两人去寻找幸福吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.01,0:17:52.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊这是豆包 跟我换
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.05,0:17:53.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.86,0:17:54.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小气鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.10,0:17:56.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗你的 给 一人一半
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.16,0:18:01.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 我们现在这样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.27,0:18:02.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.89,0:18:03.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是幸福吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.17,0:18:05.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.17,0:18:10.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前几天我给那家伙说分手了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.33,0:18:10.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他说什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.24,0:18:13.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他说你绝对会后悔的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.37,0:18:15.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活该
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.07,0:18:17.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.12,0:18:22.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸福就像大冷天的热可可一样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.89,0:18:35.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.30,0:18:37.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人耶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.89,0:18:39.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系了 他们要回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.22,0:18:41.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定会成为回忆的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.43,0:18:45.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 要是被人看到麻烦就大了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.49,0:18:47.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我今天就毕业了 无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.93,0:18:49.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还有一年呐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.97,0:18:51.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你不就出名了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.64,0:18:52.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.49,0:18:55.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.56,0:19:01.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.26,0:19:03.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想去看海
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.41,0:19:05.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啦 又冷又臭
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.32,0:19:07.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧 带我去海边
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.48,0:19:10.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好冷喔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.45,0:19:13.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌 一股海带味 跟我要的不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.26,0:19:14.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是告诉过你了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.84,0:19:16.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虫子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.08,0:19:18.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里也有 讨厌讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.35,0:19:19.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要回去 我要回去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.65,0:19:20.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是才刚到嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.03,0:19:22.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要回去 回去 回去啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.83,0:19:26.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小元 元晴君 你生气啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.66,0:19:27.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.95,0:19:32.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想看看漂亮的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.80,0:19:35.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我以后再带你去南方的海岛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.88,0:19:37.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗 什么时候
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.56,0:19:41.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实呢 要先存钱 慢慢地存 大概是十年后
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.63,0:19:42.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.55,0:19:46.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 今天只能到这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.45,0:19:47.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.48,0:19:48.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.00,0:19:49.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.14,0:19:51.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝茶嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.08,0:19:55.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咖啡可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.50,0:19:57.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.80,0:19:58.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撞到的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.49,0:20:00.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又见那家伙了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.31,0:20:04.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是见个面
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.31,0:20:11.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说了 只是见个面
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.06,0:20:12.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真过分
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.03,0:20:18.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香川 有后辈找你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.76,0:20:19.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈 后辈
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.17,0:20:25.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摔伤的？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.70,0:20:27.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能呢 你个笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.19,0:20:29.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你赢了还是输了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.53,0:20:34.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事情跟输赢没关系吧 只要揍到出气就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.72,0:20:37.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你被揍到出气了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.17,0:20:42.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.13,0:20:44.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疼啊 别碰啊 傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.81,0:20:46.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 拍张照留念吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.00,0:20:48.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你傻了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.89,0:20:51.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为这是你为我而战的印记啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.54,0:20:54.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.95,0:20:55.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.66,0:20:57.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和那个自我陶醉男一样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.38,0:21:01.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你其实很喜欢哭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.82,0:21:06.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会有人喜欢哭呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.35,0:21:08.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我现在才这么做
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.19,0:21:18.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,答应我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.15,0:21:22.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不要背叛我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.71,0:21:25.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.44,0:21:27.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会有第二次了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.42,0:21:29.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我答应你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.71,0:21:35.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我答应你 绝对不会背叛你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.13,0:21:42.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 元晴
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.52,0:21:43.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你冷静点听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.72,0:21:46.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 奈奈和香川一起开着车…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.13,0:22:11.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高桥
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.21,0:22:13.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 你醒了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.59,0:22:16.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你干吗呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.59,0:22:19.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为矢野你睡着了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.60,0:22:21.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.19,0:22:22.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把你的书包当枕头了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.91,0:22:24.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫醒我不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.92,0:22:28.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 可是看你像是在做幸福的梦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.76,0:22:31.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得把你叫醒太可怜了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.43,0:22:32.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸福的梦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.92,0:22:33.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.19,0:22:39.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸福 是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.79,0:22:42.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶 怎么说呢 很难啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.39,0:22:45.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 那个
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.99,0:22:48.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 暖和和的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.97,0:22:50.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暖和和的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.95,0:22:53.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 像肉包子啊 烤山芋之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.28,0:22:55.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在寒冷时可以取暖的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.21,0:22:57.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以让心觉得温暖的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.80,0:22:58.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肉包子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.32,0:23:02.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(424,470)}不一定啦 也可以是喜欢的书啦 CD啦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.46,0:23:04.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢的…人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.16,0:23:17.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们去吃肉包子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.60,0:23:20.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吃肉包子的季节了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.12,0:23:25.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.90,0:23:29.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(424,470)}这是我第一次祈祷别人的幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.61,0:25:07.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢的人
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.54,0:25:12.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(424,470)}最近不知怎么感觉他好像很冷淡 是我多心了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.60,0:25:15.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(424,470)}自从一起去吃肉包子那天
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.94,0:25:19.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(424,470)}你不用像刚才那样帮我说多余的话
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.97,0:25:21.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(424,470)}搞不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.62,0:25:23.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(424,470)}真搞不懂矢野你
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.40,0:25:27.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(424,470)}不能像之前那样说话了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.64,0:25:31.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(424,470)}我只说一次 你听好了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.00,0:25:34.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(424,470)}我喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.10,0:23:04.63,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}夕日が影を細く伸ばした
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.64,0:23:10.44,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}心を深く染めていく
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.88,0:23:17.10,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}きっと最後の時間だと
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.56,0:23:22.72,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}涙こらえてた
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.17,0:23:30.78,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}思い出なんていつも悲しすぎるばかり
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.88,0:23:36.80,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}いっそ忘れてしまいたいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.57,0:23:44.19,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}二度と会えない君の背中と
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.29,0:23:50.13,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}最後の夕日見つめ続けた
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.36,0:23:56.83,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}そっとそっとこぼれ落ちていく
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.09,0:24:06.06,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}今はこの雨にうたれ
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.20,0:24:14.57,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}もう泣いていいかな 君はいないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.67,0:24:21.23,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}涙あふれても止めないでいて
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.33,0:24:27.82,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}雨よ凍らせてこの心まで
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.92,0:24:37.15,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}そっとこのまま消えてしまいたいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.79,0:25:01.17,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Stop the sunset 今は歌わないでいて
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.27,0:25:07.93,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}海に落ちてゆく 悲し色ね
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.03,0:25:14.51,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}ずっとこの場所で一人にさせて
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.61,0:25:23.53,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}夕日よこのまま 沈まないでいて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.10,0:23:04.63,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}身影在落日下纤细地蔓延
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.64,0:23:10.44,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}心也被它渲染
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.88,0:23:17.10,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}你说 这注定是最后的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.56,0:23:22.72,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}我将泪水强留
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.17,0:23:30.78,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}为何回忆总是这么悲伤
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.88,0:23:36.80,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}我宁愿干脆将它遗忘
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.57,0:23:44.19,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}只能注视着你那无法再见的背影
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.29,0:23:50.13,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}和那最后的夕阳
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.36,0:23:56.83,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}静静地静静地洒落的雨滴
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.09,0:24:06.06,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}现在打在我的身上
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.20,0:24:14.57,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}你不在了 我可以哭了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.67,0:24:21.23,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}泪水止不住决堤
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.33,0:24:27.82,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}雨水啊 连我的心也冰封吧
